org.agilewiki.jactor2.util.durable

Interface Factory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Named
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppFactory, BListFactory, FactoryImpl, IncDesFactory, IntegerBMapFactory, IntegerSMapFactory, LongBMapFactory, LongSMapFactory, MapEntryFactory, SListFactory, StringBMapFactory, StringSMapFactory, TupleFactory

    public interface Factory
extends Named
    For every type of serializable object there is a factory object that creates and configures objects of that type, with the name assigned to the factory object identifying the type of serializable object.
